Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 387
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Pilgrimage-Descent Into Hell=Crossing the Flood
  - 223
By: Anagarvajra
---
Thou, O Lord, hast rescued me from the ocean of ages, vast in its
terror, and disturbed with the waves which are our births, from the
mud of molestations, which is so hard to cross.
